name: Big Brothers #18
description:
100 + 100 Big Brothers (HBB), Generative Avatar Project By Rasa Kolko


Generative Art is a process of algorithmically generating new ideas, forms, shapes, colors or patterns. First, you create rules that provide boundaries for the creation process. Then a computer follows those rules to produce new works on your behalf.  



-

 A few noses, a few eyebrows, a few eyes and a few mustaches have formed 100 different rare characters that we see in this Generative avatar project.

 

 have tried to make the production of this project as delicate as a traditional artwork.



100 are colorful.

100 are Black & Red.

-

Hope you enjoy!
